    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Apr 12, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-04-12/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Apr 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-04-12/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Spy toys: A look at the dangers of data breaches in toys&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With so many toys connected to the internet it&amp;rsquo;s no wonder hackers are targeting toys. Now that Spiral Toys has been involved in a data breach, Jade &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.toynews-online.biz/business-analysis/read/spy-toys-a-look-at-the-dangers-of-data-breaches-in-toys/048464&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.toynews-online.biz/business-analysis/read/spy-toys-a-look-at-the-dangers-of-data-breaches-in-toys/048464&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Endpoint Detection and Response Solutions Reviews&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Community presented by Gartner Peer Insights.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.gartner.com/reviews/market/Endpoint-Detection-and-Response-Solutions&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.gartner.com/reviews/market/Endpoint-Detection-and-Response-Solutions&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data Sheds Light on MSP&amp;rsquo;s Favorite Vendors&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Among companies that made last year&amp;rsquo;s MSPmentor 501 list of top managed service providers, Webroot was the preferred endpoint protection &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://mspmentor.net/msp-mentor/data-sheds-light-msp-s-favorite-vendors&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://mspmentor.net/msp-mentor/data-sheds-light-msp-s-favorite-vendors&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Share prices &amp;lsquo;suffer 1.8% drop following data breaches&amp;rsquo;, says report&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now an analysis of new data claims to show that investors and analysts are starting to &amp;lsquo;price in&amp;rsquo; data breaches when valuing companies.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.scmagazineuk.com/share-prices-suffer-18-drop-following-data-breaches-says-report/article/649863/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.scmagazineuk.com/share-prices-suffer-18-drop-following-data-breaches-says-report/article/649863/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Connecting previous Endpoint clients to new Sophos UTM install&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;issues. I have a heap of Windows clients with the Sophos Endpoint virus &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://community.sophos.com/products/unified-threat-management/f/endpoint-protection-antivirus-and-device-control/90841/connecting-previous-endpoint-clients-to-new-sophos-utm-install&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://community.sophos.com/products/unified-threat-management/f/endpoint-protection-antivirus-and-device-control/90841/connecting-previous-endpoint-clients-to-new-sophos-utm-install&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Telecommuting Healthcare Employees Get Employers in HIPAA Compliance Hot&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lexology (registration) Covered entities are required to self-report data breaches to the Office for Civil Rights (OCR), the agency charged with enforcing the HIPAA Privacy &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.lexology.com/library/detail.aspx?g=fb47e04e-e328-40bf-a541-399cd369709d&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.lexology.com/library/detail.aspx?g=fb47e04e-e328-40bf-a541-399cd369709d&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Tax Identity Theft Surges On Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Tax day is just a week away, but as you hurry to get your return in, experts say you must also take more care than ever to protect your identity. You&amp;rsquo;ve &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://wnpr.org/post/tax-identity-theft-surges-data-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://wnpr.org/post/tax-identity-theft-surges-data-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Crunch time for Yahoo as EU prepares to release statement on data breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Irish data protection authority (DPA) is preparing to release the findings of an investigation into the data breaches that occurred at Yahoo, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.v3.co.uk/v3-uk/news/3008305/crunch-time-for-yahoo-as-eu-prepares-to-release-statement-on-data-breaches&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.v3.co.uk/v3-uk/news/3008305/crunch-time-for-yahoo-as-eu-prepares-to-release-statement-on-data-breaches&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cybersecurity Attacks Hit 87% of Organizations in 2016&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Healthcare cybersecurity attacks are also on the rise, with PHI data breaches continuing to affect organizations of all sizes. A Redspin report released &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://healthitsecurity.com/news/cybersecurity-attacks-hit-87-of-organizations-in-2016&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://healthitsecurity.com/news/cybersecurity-attacks-hit-87-of-organizations-in-2016&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo&amp;rsquo;s EU Watchdog set to show teeth as privacy probe wraps up&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Inc. is set to be ordered to make changes as its chief privacy regulator in Europe wraps up a probe into one of the biggest data breaches in history.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://indianexpress.com/article/technology/tech-news-technology/yahoos-eu-watchdog-set-to-show-teeth-as-privacy-probe-wraps-up-4609270/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://indianexpress.com/article/technology/tech-news-technology/yahoos-eu-watchdog-set-to-show-teeth-as-privacy-probe-wraps-up-4609270/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Data breaches strip tens of millions off UK firms&amp;rsquo; market value, study&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ComputerWeekly.com A good example of the effects of data breaches on company value is Yahoo, which was forced to discount by $350m the sale price of its core business &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.computerweekly.com/news/450416724/Data-breaches-strip-tens-of-millions-off-UK-firms-market-value-study-shows&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.computerweekly.com/news/450416724/Data-breaches-strip-tens-of-millions-off-UK-firms-market-value-study-shows&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;SentinelOne Appoints Seasoned Sales Executive to Lead Worldwide Channels&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo Finance PALO ALTO, CA&amp;ndash;(Marketwired - Apr 12, 2017) - SentinelOne, the company transforming endpoint protection by delivering unified, multi-layer &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/sentinelone-appoints-seasoned-sales-executive-150000097.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/sentinelone-appoints-seasoned-sales-executive-150000097.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;A credible threat: cyber attacks and stolen credentials&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;63% of all breaches involved the use of stolen credentials, which is a huge element that cannot be stopped by network or endpoint security.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.information-age.com/credible-threat-cyber-attacks-stolen-credentials-123465723/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.information-age.com/credible-threat-cyber-attacks-stolen-credentials-123465723/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Targeting the Weak Link in the Supply Chain: Amazon Third-Party Sellers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;eSecurity Planet &amp;hellip; method of authentication to verify the user&amp;rsquo;s identity for a login or other transaction, in order to stop the use of stolen credentials,&amp;rdquo; Williams added.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.esecurityplanet.com/network-security/amazon-sellers-hacked-targeting-the-weak-link-in-the-supply-chain.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.esecurityplanet.com/network-security/amazon-sellers-hacked-targeting-the-weak-link-in-the-supply-chain.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;What Happens To Your Information After A Data Breach?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data breaches have become all-too-common amongst retailers, businesses, educational institutions and health care facilities. Last year, 1,093 data &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.business2community.com/cybersecurity/happens-information-data-breach-01819065&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.business2community.com/cybersecurity/happens-information-data-breach-01819065&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Automation is the key to better enterprise security&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;People are no longer surprised by data breaches. Many breaches are perpetrated by malicious actors. Others are the result of lapses in internal &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itproportal.com/news/automation-is-the-key-to-better-enterprise-security/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itproportal.com/news/automation-is-the-key-to-better-enterprise-security/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;10 of the biggest healthcare data breaches announced in Q1&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As of March 14, there have been 312 reported data breaches and more than 1.3 million exposed records in 2017, according to the Identity Theft &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.beckershospitalreview.com/healthcare-information-technology/10-of-the-biggest-healthcare-data-breaches-announced-in-q1.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.beckershospitalreview.com/healthcare-information-technology/10-of-the-biggest-healthcare-data-breaches-announced-in-q1.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The growing difficulty of protecting data on the move&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is also the link between data breaches themselves and terrorism. Often, cyber security breaches in particular but also data breaches involving &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.itproportal.com/features/the-growing-difficulty-of-protecting-data-on-the-move/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.itproportal.com/features/the-growing-difficulty-of-protecting-data-on-the-move/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;A Look at Facebook&amp;rsquo;s Interactive Neural Network Visualization System&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; there are other problems with this lack of insight into network behavior, particularly in terms of optimizing models for better performance, efficiency, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nextplatform.com/2017/04/12/look-facebooks-interactive-neural-network-visualization-system/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.nextplatform.com/2017/04/12/look-facebooks-interactive-neural-network-visualization-system/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;In Cyberspace, It&amp;rsquo;s Always Hunting Season&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The confluence of cyber defense and offense has given rise to the practice of threat hunting: aggressively seeking adversaries rather than waiting to &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.afcea.org/content/?q=cyberspace-it%E2%80%99s-always-hunting-season&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.afcea.org/content/?q=cyberspace-it%E2%80%99s-always-hunting-season&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;5 lessons to avoid credential theft&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nearly every breach uses stolen credentials. According the 2016 Verizon Data Breach Incident Report, 63 per cent of breaches have used stolen &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mybusiness.com.au/technology/2877-5-lessons-to-avoid-credential-theft&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.mybusiness.com.au/technology/2877-5-lessons-to-avoid-credential-theft&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
